            <abstract>
            <p>This hymn is ascribed to John Chrysostom. The hymn begins with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈሥሒ፡ ኦእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>, which is repeated after each stanza.
                In most manuscripts, it occurs in a longer version, where the hymn is preceded by a preamble varying in structure and length, beginning with <foreign xml:lang="gez">እሰግድ፡ ለኪ፡ ወእዌድሰኪ፡ ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>.</p>
